                                    BetCoin

Use of Metamask:-

                  Metamask is used as the digital wallet to take away the complexicity of desiging a home grown digital wallet system which require external database or resources within betcoin network.  By adopting metamask, network user creation, maintenance, book keeping and
listing out transactions are moved out of betcoin app which makes the network lean and gas usage friendly which makes more attractive to community users and makes the token value higher.


Use of ERC20 specification

		Making BetCoin as an ERC20 token system, its becomes very attractive to community users where they can trade the RAM tokens for any other lucreative token( Interoperability) available on the network.  






